\par\plain {\f0\fs20\b0\i0 AUTHORS:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs20\b0\i0 \bullet  Discuss authorship and develop a written authorship document (including lead authorship) at an early stage during a project.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs20\b0\i0 \bullet  Check and follow ICMJE criteria on contributorship and authorship. (http://www.icmje.org/recommendations/browse/roles-and-responsibilities/defining-the-role-of-authors-and-contributors.html)}
